rom the\ndirection of the solar motion due to a tidal stream could be detected with of\norder a hundred events, regardless of whether the sense of the recoils is\nknown.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Aug 2004 13:14:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 May 2005 15:32:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-11-19"}
