 not\nbecause entropy is produced, but because black holes classically are perfect\nabsorbers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Aug 2004 08:39:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Nov 2004 12:17:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
