e discuss main\nfeatures of the large nu case, which corresponds for nu -> infty to a\ndecoupling of heavy Higgs bosons.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Aug 2004 18:40:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Mar 2005 05:32:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 1 Aug 2005 08:58:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-07-19"}
